Overview

This project implements a Recommendation System using Collaborative Filtering. 
The model predicts user preferences based on historical interactions and provides personalized recommendations. 
Collaborative filtering leverages the similarity between users or items to generate suggestions, making it one of the most widely used approaches in industry 
(e.g., Netflix, Amazon, Spotify).

Features

User-based and Item-based Collaborative Filtering
Matrix Factorization (optional if included in your notebook)
Handles missing ratings with similarity-based predictions
Generates top-N recommendations for users
Jupyter Notebook with step-by-step explanation
